Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1196,432)}爱丽耶丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1164.6,491.2)}卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1163,553.6)}札克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,带着萤光真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它喊好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎  刚刚是小福妮的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  改良过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么没价值的改良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,评判是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是按谁的标准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吃过所有美食合在一起的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定夸大其词了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫它糖果草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,收集下这附近长的  给大家都尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真哒好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃多少了啊  爱丽耶丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,札克啊  也来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,口气别跟我妈似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是卫星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到这么激动人心的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙真太伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个仙人球里面果然都是水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(210,882)\pos(1054.2,107.2)}水源调查组
