Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,885)\pos(1156.6,254.4)}夏鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,885)\pos(1158.2,294.4)}金德莉
